column18:
Welcome to a study about impression formation


 

This study involves appraising people based on short descriptions. We estimate that the total amount of time to complete the study is approximately 5-10 minutes.
As this study is a preliminary test of material to be used in a later experiment, you will also be asked a few questions about your experiences completing the survey.


 

The corresponding author is Elli van Berlekom, a PhD candidate at Stockholm University. For further inquiries, please email the following address: elli.vanberlekom@psychology.su.se.
Any data you input will be saved and used for research, but your response will be completely anonymous. Any results will only be published at the group level.
